short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Meet Pro is designed to simplify the process of creating Google Meet links by adding a new menu item in Chrome.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Meet Pro is designed to simplify the process of creating Google Meet links by adding a new menu item in Chrome. Once installed, users can easily generate a new Meet link by clicking on a menu item or on the extension icon in their browser.
